column5: Any major delays along the way? Traveling from Indianapolis to Bloomington, IL to Rockford to Duluth to International Falls to Sioux Lookout.

I can't say about how your trip to Il. will be, but we left Peoria last Friday am, drove to FF, and then on the Ear Falls. The only construction that slowed us down was on the causeway leaving FF, that was less than 5 min. Hopefully the roads for you will just as open! Good luck!
